reviewText: Bought this Season1 and Season 2 for a birthday gift. Since my hubby and I love these series, it was wonderful gift for someone who loves histories and its hidden secrets. Good Show!
Title: Mysteries At The Museum Season 1

reviewText: most informational program that is on tv today. It takes you to little known thing in museums around the United States.
Title: Mysteries At The Museum Season 1

reviewText: I just finished watching Season 1 and while I found it interesting, it didn't go deep enough into the things I liked and there were things that I had no interest in at all. I bought season 2 so I will watch it, but I don't think I'll purchase furhter seasons.
Title: Mysteries At The Museum Season 1

reviewText: JUST A GREAT SERIES FOR THE WHOLE FAMILY AND ANYONE WHO IS A HISTORY BUFF...LEARN ABOUT THINGS YOU NEVER NEW HAPPENED.....BUY IT!!!
Title: Mysteries At The Museum Season 1

reviewText: Here is a cool video to learn what is out there in local museums that you may not even know of.  I learned a lot about museums I have been to and didn't even know what I was seeing.  A must for any museum geek give it a try
summary: Great show and a lot to learn
Title: Mysteries At The Museum Season 1
